                                subscription_number_pk, latest_point, restart_at, completed
                           FROM (SELECT ap_grade, ap_end_dt, eventid, apref, start_date, end_date, completion_date, lesson_number, lock_assignment, segment_id_fk, subject, subject_id_fk, assignType,

                                        book_item_number, image_url, ap_credt, teacher, sub_start_date, sortorder,
                                        sessionsrequired, sessionoptioncount, min(sessionRemaining) OVER (PARTITION BY subject_id_fk, supergroup, lesson_number) AS requirementsRemaining,
                                        subscription_number_pk, latest_point, restart_at, completed
                                   FROM (SELECT ap_grade, ap_end_dt, assign.student_assignments_id AS eventID, assign.apref, assign.start_date, assign.end_date, assign.completion_date, segments.lesson AS lesson_number,
                                                assign.lock_assignment, assign.segment_id_fk, assign.subject, assign.subject_id_fk,
                                                CASE mediatypes.name
                                                    WHEN 'STREAMING' THEN 'LESSON'
                                                    ELSE 'DVD'
                                                END AS assignType,
                                                sessions.sessionname AS short_description, 'Lesson ' || segments.lesson AS long_description, assign.da_testassignmentid,
                                                assign.pr_form, assign.pr_version, assign.pr_school, assign.pr_boxletter, assign.pr_itemnumber, COALESCE(assign.pr_subitemnumber, 0) AS pr_subitemnumber,
                                                subjects.grade, to_number(subjects.book_item_number) AS book_item_number, subjects.image_url, appld.ap_credt,
                                                CASE
                                                    WHEN NVL(title.ttitl_nbr, 0) IN (3, 9, 10, 20, 21) THEN NVL(title.ttitledesc,'') || ' ' || NVL(teacher.teacher_last_name,'')
                                                    ELSE NVL(title.ttitledesc,'') || '. ' || NVL(teacher.teacher_last_name,'')
                                                END AS teacher, subs.start_date AS sub_start_date, sessions.sortorder, COALESCE(sessions.supergroup, sessions.sessiontype) AS supergroup, segments.sessionsrequired, segments.sessionoptioncount,

                                                    WHEN assign.completion_date IS NOT NULL THEN 0

                                                CASE
                                                    WHEN uitems.completed IS NULL THEN
                                                        CASE
                                                            WHEN assign.completion_date IS NOT NULL THEN 'Y'
                                                            ELSE 'N'
                                                        END
                                                    ELSE COALESCE(uitems.completed, 'N')
                                                END AS completed
                                           FROM studentAssignments assign
                                           JOIN abadb.appld
                                             ON assign.apref = appld.ap_apref
                                           JOIN abashared.vlessonsegmentrequirements segments
                                             ON assign.segment_id_fk = segments.segmentid
                                           JOIN abashared.vsessiontypes sessions
                                             ON segments.sessiontypeid = sessions.sessiontypeid
                                           JOIN abashared.vsubjects subjects
                                             ON subjects.subjectid = assign.subject_id_fk
                                           -- streaming only? use JOIN
                                           -- with DVDs? use LEFT JOIN
                                           JOIN abashared.streaming_subscriptions subs
                                             ON assign.apref = subs.application_number
                                           -- streaming only? use JOIN
                                           -- with DVDs? use LEFT JOIN                                    
                                           JOIN abashared.streaming_subscriptions_items subitems
                                             ON subs.subscription_number_pk = subitems.subscription_number_fk
                                            AND subitems.subject_id_fk = assign.subject_id_fk
                                      LEFT JOIN abashared.streaming_users_items uitems
                                             ON uitems.subscription_items_fk = subitems.subscription_items_pk
                                            AND uitems.segment_id_fk = segments.segmentid
                                      LEFT JOIN abashared.teacher_subjects teacher_sbj
                                             ON teacher_sbj.subject_id_fk = segments.subjectid
                                      LEFT JOIN abashared.teachers teacher
                                             ON teacher.teacher_pk = teacher_sbj.teacher_pk_fk
                                           JOIN abadb.ttitl title
                                             ON title.ttitl_nbr = teacher.teacher_title
                                      LEFT JOIN abashared.unfinished_rchdr urchdr
                                             ON appld.ap_apref = urchdr.rch_apref
                                           JOIN enrollment.media_format_types@abadb mediatypes
                                             ON mediatypes.media_format_type_id = appld.media_format_type_id
                                          WHERE (subs.subscription_status_fk = 1
                                                    OR subs.subscription_status_fk IS NULL
                                                    OR mediatypes.name != 'STREAMING')
                                            AND (sessions.subject_group = subitems.subject_group
                                                    OR subitems.subject_group IS NULL
                                                    OR sessions.subject_group IS NULL
                                                    OR uitems.completed = 'Y')

                                                    OR (mediatypes.name != 'STREAMING' AND (TRUNC(SYSDATE) BETWEEN to_date(appld.ap_beg_dt, 'yyyymmdd') - 14  AND COALESCE(appld.ap_end_dt, trunc(sysdate)) ) ) )
                                            AND (segments.lesson BETWEEN subitems.start_lesson_number and subitems.end_lesson_number
                                                    OR subs.subscription_status_fk IS NULL
                                                    OR mediatypes.name != 'STREAMING')
                                            AND (urchdr.rch_status IN ('A', 'I')
                                                    OR appld.ap_credt != 'Y')
                                            AND (sessions.pen_key = appld.pen_key OR sessions.pen_key IS NULL)
                                            AND appld.ap_status = 8
                                        )
                                )

    nextLessonsMinLesson AS (SELECT DISTINCT assign.ap_end_dt, assign.ap_grade, assign.subject_id_fk, assign.apref, MIN(assign.lesson_number) OVER(PARTITION BY assign.subject_id_fk) AS nextLesson, MIN(assign.lesson_number) OVER(PARTITION BY assign.apref) AS minLesson
                               FROM videoAssignments assign
                              WHERE assign.completion_date IS NULL

                           GROUP BY assign.ap_grade, assign.ap_end_dt, assign.subject_id_fk, assign.apref, assign.lesson_number),

                               FROM videoAssignments assign

                                AND assign.IsRequirementMet = 'Y'
                           GROUP BY assign.ap_grade, assign.ap_end_dt, assign.subject_id_fk, assign.lesson_number)
                           
    SELECT vAssign.ap_grade, vAssign.ap_end_dt, vAssign.apref, vAssign.eventID AS eventID, vAssign.start_date, vAssign.end_date, vAssign.short_description, vAssign.long_description, vAssign.completion_date,

           vAssign.pr_form, vAssign.pr_version, vAssign.pr_school, vAssign.pr_boxletter, vAssign.pr_itemnumber, vAssign.pr_subitemnumber, CAST(vAssign.sortorder AS NUMBER(3)) AS sortorder, vAssign.lesson_number,

           vAssign.requirementsRemaining, vAssign.IsRequirementMet
      FROM videoAssignments vAssign
 LEFT JOIN lastCompletedLessons lCL
        ON vAssign.subject_id_fk = lCL.subject_id_fk
 LEFT JOIN nextLessonsMinLesson nLML
        ON vAssign.subject_id_fk = nLML.subject_id_fk
       AND vAssign.apref = nLML.apref
     WHERE vAssign.lesson_number = CASE
                                       WHEN (vAssign.grade IN(14,15,1,2,3,4,5,6) AND 'N' = ' ') OR 'N' = 'Y' THEN nLmL.minLesson
                                       WHEN (vAssign.grade IN(7,8,9,10,11,12) AND 'N' = ' ') OR 'N' = 'N' THEN nLmL.nextLesson
                                   END
        OR (vAssign.grade IN(7,8,9,10,11,12) AND trunc(vAssign.completion_date) = trunc(sysdate) )
  ORDER BY vAssign.completion_date desc, vAssign.sub_start_date, vAssign.sortorder, vAssign.lesson_number
